short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Receive an alert when FrenchBalut is live.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
FrenchBalut is a Philippines based Streamer who entertains his audience through videos and lives primarily on Twitch and YouTube. 

The extension allows access to the last 2 YouTube videos of the FrenchBalut Streamer and to be notified at the start of the stream or when a new video is released.
A video part will allow you to quickly consult the latest releases of the channel. In addition you will find all the links to the social networks of FrenchBalut.

Once installed, all new streams and new videos will trigger a notification on your computer and with a simple click you will have easy and quick access to the content.
